datasets.name: Kuzu Demo
datasets.description: The Kuzu Demo dataset is a small dataset used in the "Create your first graph" tutorial. It contains 7 nodes and 8 relationships.

datasets.name: TinySNB
datasets.description: Internal dataset used for testing. Covers most data types but is very small.

datasets.name: LDBC SNB Scale Factor 0.1
datasets.description: The standard LDBC SNB dataset with a scale factor of 0.1 (visit https://ldbcouncil.org/benchmarks/snb/ for more information).

datasets.name: SNAP Amazon
datasets.description: Amazon product co-purchasing network dataset (visit https://snap.stanford.edu/data/com-Amazon.html for more information).

datasets.name: SNAP Twitter
datasets.description: Twitter social circles dataset (visit https://snap.stanford.edu/data/ego-Twitter.html for more information).
